Game ........: Toy Racer
Date .....: 2004.04.10 
Ripped by ...: DCP (Nothing)
 Video ....: PAL

On your marks and get set for Toy Racer, as you and up to three players take control in the miniaturized world that is Toy Racer, be the first to cross the finish line but who says you need to play fair! Race against friends or challenge thousands of other 
players across Europe On-Line! Featuring four crazy tracks, over twenty-four vehicles, lots of weapons and bonuses on each track. Who says size matters? 